::Diamond::

She started coming around and put her hand to her forhead, feeling a 
bump just above her left eye.  She slowly opened up her eyes and 
looked up at Devilduer. She was still alittle  out of hit.  She 
looked at him and closed her eyes, sighing. "OK, who are you and why 
are you carrying me? And after that...what happened?" She leaned ehr 
head against his shoulder and tried to think about how she ended up 
in this bots arms and what happened to her ship?  She couldn't 
remember anything after the ship started getting cought in the black 
hole's gravitation  pull.  She passed out again and went limp in his 
arms.
